Package edu.rit.m2mi.test

Package edu.rit.m2mi.test contains unit test programs for the M2MI Layer in package edu.rit.m2mi.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ArrayProcessor Interface ArrayProcessor specifies the interface for an exported object that processes an array of integers.
Bar Interface Bar is a target interface for testing handles and method invokers.
Countdown Interface Countdown specifies the interface for an exported object used to measure M2MI invocation timing.
Ping Interface Ping specifies the interface for an exported object used to test M2MI invocations and measure M2MI invocation timing.
Pong Interface Pong specifies the interface for an exported object used to test M2MI invocations and measure M2MI invocation timing.
 

Class Summary
ArrayProcessorTest01 Class ArrayProcessorTest01 is a main program for testing M2MI.
ArrayProcessorTest02 Class ArrayProcessorTest02 is a main program for testing M2MI.
BarImpl Class BarImpl provides an implementation of target interface Bar for testing handles and method invokers.
BarImpl2 Class BarImpl2 provides an implementation of target interface Bar for testing handles and method invokers.
CountdownImpl01 Class CountdownImpl01 provides an exported object used to measure M2MI invocation timing.
CountdownTest01 Class CountdownTesti01 is a main program to measure M2MI invocation timing.
NI Class NI is a main program that prints out all the network interfaces and their IP addresses on the device.
Pinger Class Pinger is a main program used to test M2MI invocations and measure M2MI invocation timing.
Ponger Class Ponger is a main program used to test M2MI invocations and measure M2MI invocation timing.
Test01 Class Test01 is a unit test main program for testing synthesized method invokers.
Test02 Class Test02 is a unit test main program for testing class Invocation.
Test03 Class Test03 is a unit test main program for testing class Invocation.
Test04 Class Test04 is a unit test main program for testing class Invocation.
Test05 Class Test05 is a unit test main program for testing M2MI omnihandles.
Test06 Class Test06 is a unit test main program for testing M2MI omnihandles and multihandles.
Test07 Class Test07 is a unit test main program for testing M2MI omnihandles, multihandles, and unihandles.
